# Pre-deployment audit (Lighthouse targets)
performance:
  - First Contentful Paint: < 1.2s
  - Largest Contentful Paint: < 2.0s
  - Cumulative Layout Shift: < 0.1
  - Total Blocking Time: < 200ms

accessibility:
  - WCAG 2.2 AA: 100% pass rate
  - Color contrast: ≥ 4.5:1 (text), ≥ 3:1 (UI)
  - Keyboard navigation: fully operable
  - ARIA landmarks: properly implemented

seo:
  - Structured data validated
  - Mobile-friendly test: pass
  - Canonical URLs: configured
  - robots.txt: allow institutional crawlers

security:
  - HTTPS enforced (Cloudflare/GitHub Pages auto)
  - CSP header (optional for static): default-src 'self'
  - Subresource Integrity for external scripts
